#FUNCTION
PING target host in loop, record the min/max/average time of each ping
#CONFIG
First config the "samplehost.txt", each line is one target host IP/domain.
Then config the "pingconfig", mainly sTime,OUT,hostIP. sTime is the interval time for each loop, OUT is the direct of the result file,hostip is the local IP.
#USE
USE "./pingtest.sh" to run, ctrl z to quit. 
The result will be shown in "pingresult.txt"
